name: Veganie
description: Independent, all-vegan beauty care and cosmetics shop est. since 2015 (originally known as Vegan Mania). Features a natural and cruelty-free range of products like body lotion and oils, lip balms, make-up, and nail polish. Open Mon 11:00-19:00, Tue-Sat 10:00-19:00. Closed Sun.

name: Hank Vegan Burger - Archives
description: Hank's flagship location est. since 2013. Features a menu of burgers which are all vegan and delicious. Feb 2019 reported Beyond Burger available. Burgers are served alongside fries, small salads, cookies, and beer. Open Mon-Fri 12:00-22:00, Sat 12:00-23:00, Sun 12:00-22:00.

name: Happiz - Monge
description: The second branch of this vegetarian pizzeria opened Jan 2019. Features create-your-own pizzas. Offers mock meats (ham, merguez, salami, chorizo), beyond meat steak pieces, and a variety of fresh vegetable toppings. Has vegan mozzarella cheese. For dessert try the chocolate mousse pot or vegan tiramisu. Open Mon-Sat 11:30-14:30, 18:30-22:30, Sun 11:30-22:30. Closed Mon.

name: Hank Vegan Pizza
description: A vegan pizza shop est. 2016 by Hank Vegan Burger. Offers daily variety of pizzas, which are available by the slice: choose which you'd like. Also serves drinks, salad, and desserts. Seating on two floors. Open Mon-Sun 12:00-22:00.

name: Cloud Cakes
description: Vegan coffee shop and bakery near Chatelet-Les Halles station, since 2016. Specialty is cupcakes. Serves coffee and drinks, a selection of light meals, and of course, vegan croissants and pastries. Offers breakfast Monday through Saturday and brunch on Sunday. Lunch is served till 3pm. Open Mon-Fri 09:00-19:00, Sat 09:30-19:00, Sun 11:30-15:30.

name: Wholywood
description: Vegan cafe serving organic food and craft coffee. Features fusion bowls, burgers, sandwiches, "crazy waffles" and other daily selection of fresh baked pastries plus juices and drinks - since May 2019. Plastic-free. Note that some food may start to sell out after 5pm and may close earlier than stated times. Open Mon 09:00-18:00, 10:00-18:00, Wed-Sat 09:00-18:00.

name: Biovégane
description: Healthy vegan burger bar set in a pedestrian area. Can accommodate 10 on the heated terrace and 6 inside. Offering 100% organic and handmade food with gluten-free options. Customise your burger with preferred garnish such as vegan "bacon" or seaweed. Fries are not fried but roasted in the oven with little oil. Est. 2018 formerly as VeganBioBurger and GABY. Open Mon 12:00-14:30, 18:30-21:00, Wed-Fri 12:00-14:30, Wed 18:30-21:00, Thu-Sun 18:30-22:00, Sat-Sun 12:00-15:00.

name: Burger Theory
address: 11 Blvd des Filles du Calvaire, Paris, France, 750…
description: Fast food vegan restaurant opened Sep 2018 in Paris 3rd arrisdonment. Serves multiple flavors of plant-based burgers in addition to accompaniments like fries, salad, and soup of the day. For dessert try the vegan brownie. Combo meal of burger with side, drink, and dessert available. Open Mon-Tue 12:00-15:00, Wed-Sun 12:00-22:00.

name: Un Monde Vegan
address: 64 rue Notre Dame de Nazareth, Paris, France, 7500…
description: Un Monde Vegan, meaning "a vegan world," is a 100% vegan retail shop as well as an online store. Features a wide range of plant-based products including packaged and chilled foods, faux meats, vegan cheese, snacks and chocolates. Also has nutritional supplements, food for animals, eco-friendly cleaning and bodycare products. Established since 2009. Open Mon-Tue 11:00-20:00, Wed-Sat 10:00-20:00.

name: Aujourd'hui Demain
description: Vegan concept store & restaurant-cafe est. 2017. Serves Cali inspired lunch foods from 10am-3pm with toasts and seasonal bowls, classic blt cheeseburger w/ beyond meat, and a "fried chicky" burger. In the evenings Tue-Sat from 6pm a Mexican menu is available. On the weekends there is brunch. The coffee shop offers granola bowls, pancakes, latte drinks, juices, and gluten-free pastries. In the store you will find clothing, accessories, books, natural beauty products, and select groceries for sale. Open Tue-Sat 10:00-22:30, Sun 11:00-18:00. Closed Mon.

name: Hot Vog
description: Takeaway vegan eatery with a small seating area, est. 2017 across from the Luxembourg Gardens. Specializes in hot vogs which are vegan hot dogs. Offers also sweets like waffles as well as fresh juices and chilled bottled beverages. Hot Vog also operates food trucks/carts parked at Jardim d'Acclimatation, Parly2 at Le Chesnay, Aeroville, and Grande Épicerie rue de Passy malls. Open Mon-Sun 11:00-20:00. Closes early sometimes.
